msgid "Apply for funding to save an asset in your community"
msgstr "Gwneud cais am gyllid i achub ased yn eich cymuned"

#: frontend/magic_links/filters.py:8
msgid "at"
msgstr "am"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:7
msgid "Community Ownership Fund"
msgstr "Y Gronfa Perchnogaeth Gymunedol"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:12
msgid "Submission deadline:"
msgstr "Dyddiad cau cyflwyno:"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:16
msgid "Continue"
msgstr "Parhau"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:21
msgid "How to complete your application"
msgstr "Sut i gwblhau eich cais"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:23
msgid "Moving through the form"
msgstr "Symud drwy'r ffurflen"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:24
msgid "This form is split into sections based on how it will be assessed."
msgstr "Mae'r ffurflen wedi'i rhannu yn adrannau ar sail y modd y caiff ei hasesu."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:25
msgid "You do not have to complete it in order, or all at once."
msgstr "Nid oes rhaid i chi ei llenwi mewn trefn, na'r cyfan ar unwaith."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:27
msgid "You can preview the"
msgstr "Gallwch gael cip ymlaen llaw o'r"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:28
msgid "full list of application questions."
msgstr "rhestr lawn o gwestiynau."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:31
msgid ""
"When you have written something in every field in a section, the section "
"will be marked as complete. You can still\n"
"      change your responses in sections that are marked as complete."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch wedi ysgrifennu rhywbeth ym mhob maes mewn adran, cofnodir yr"
" adran fel un gyflawn. Gallwch newid eich\n"
"      ymatebion o hyd mewn adrannau sydd wedi'u cofnodi fel rhai cyflawn."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:36
msgid "Saving progress and making changes"
msgstr "Cadw cynnydd a gwneud newidiadau"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:38
msgid ""
"Your work will not save automatically. To make sure you do not lose "
"anything, select <strong>Save and\n"
"        continue</strong> regularly, and always before you go back or "
"close your internet browser window."
msgstr ""
"Ni fydd eich gwaith yn cael ei gadw'n awtomatig. I wneud yn siŵr nad "
"ydych chi'n colli unrhyw beth, dewiswch <strong>Cadw a \n"
"        pharhau</strong> yn rheolaidd, a bob amser cyn i chi fynd yn ôl "
"neu gau eich ffenestr porwr rhyngrwyd."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:41
msgid "If you need to edit or revisit any sections, use the browser back button."
msgstr ""
"Os oes angen i chi olygu neu fynd yn ôl at unrhyw adrannau, defnyddiwch "
"fotwm nôl y porwr."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:43
msgid "You can edit your responses as many times as you like before you submit."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch olygu'ch ymatebion gymaint o weithiau a fynnwch cyn i chi eu "
"cyflwyno."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:47
msgid "Submitting your application"
msgstr "Cyflwyno'ch cais"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:49
msgid ""
"When you have completed all sections, you’ll be able to submit your\n"
"      application."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch wedi llenwi'r holl adrannau, byddwch yn gallu cyflwyno'ch "
"cais."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:53
msgid ""
"Once you have submitted your application, you’ll not be able to edit, add"
"\n"
"      or change any sections."
msgstr ""
"Wedi i chi gyflwyno'ch cais, ni fyddwch yn gallu golygu, ychwanegu\n"
"      na newid unrhyw adrannau."

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:57
msgid "Get help"
msgstr "Cael help"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:59
msgid "If you have questions about the form or the fund, email us at"
msgstr ""
"Os oes gennych unrhyw gwestiynau ynglŷn â'r ffurflen neu'r gronfa, "
"anfonwch e-bost atom yn"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:62
msgid "How we'll use your information"
msgstr "Sut byddwn ni'n defnyddio'ch gwybodaeth"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:64
msgid "Read how we'll use the information from your application in our"
msgstr ""
"Darllenwch sut byddwn ni'n defnyddio'r wybodaeth o'ch cais yn ein "
"hysbysiad preifatrwydd"

#: frontend/magic_links/templates/landing.html:66
msgid "privacy notice"
msgstr "hysbysiad preifatrwydd"

#: frontend/templates/footer.html:9
msgid "Privacy"
msgstr "Preifatrwydd"

#: frontend/templates/footer.html:14
msgid "Cookies"
msgstr "Cwcis"

#: frontend/templates/footer.html:18
msgid "Accessibility Statement"
msgstr "Datganiad Hygyrchedd"

#: frontend/templates/footer.html:22
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Cysylltwch â ni"

